 State Football || [[Division III (NCAA)|III]] || Jason Mangone || 9-3 ||[[2019 NCAA Division III football season|2019 Division III Playoffs 2nd Round]]|| Muhlenberg || 0 || 42 ||[https://www.discoverlehighvalley.com/listing/scotty-wood-stadium-muhlenberg-college/3041/ Scotty Wood Stadium]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"#FFC425\" |<span style=\"color:white;\"> '''Total NCAA Playoff Games'''</span>\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"#FFC425\" | <span style=\"color:white;\"> '''14'''</span>\n|- align=\"center\"\n|}\n\n==Notable former players==\nNotable alumni include:\n\n[[Josh Warner]] [[Chicago Bears]] (2002\u20132003)\n\nJay Johnson [[Pittsburgh Steelers]] (2002), [[Rhein Fire]] (2003)\n\nJoe Scibilia Dauphins de Nice French Football League (2013)\n\n==Year-by-year results==\n:''Statistics correct as of the end of the 2016 college football season''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|bgcolor=\"#F2F5AC\"|<small>'''[[NCAA Division III National Football Championship|NCAA Division III Playoff Berth]]'''</small>\n|bgcolor=\"#DDFFDD\"|<small>'''Conference Champions'''</small>\n|bgcolor=\"#D0E7FF\"|<small>'''Division Champions'''</small>\n|bgcolor=\"#EBA4A4\"|<small>'''Undefeated Season'''</small>\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\" width=85%\n|-\n! rowspan=2|Year\n! rowspan=2|NCAA Division\n! rowspan=2|Conference\n! colspan=\"5\"|Overall\n! colspan=\"6\"|Conference\n! rowspan=2|Coach\n|-\n! Games !! Win !! Loss !! Tie !! Pct.\n! Games !! Win !! Loss !! Tie !! Pct. !! Standing\n|- \n| 2004 || [[Division III (NCAA)|III]] || [[Atlantic Central Football Conference|ACFC]] || 10 || 6 || 4 || 0 || .600 || 5 || 3 || 2 || 0 || .600 || 3rd || [[Rocco Salomone]]\n|- \n| 2005 || [[Division III (NCAA)|III]] || [[Atlantic Central Football Conference|ACFC]] || 10 || 5 || 5 || 0 || .500 || 5 || 4 || 1 || 0 || .800 || 3rd || Rocco Salomone\n|- \n| 2006 || [[Division III (NCAA)|III]] || [[Atlantic Central Football Conference|ACFC]] || 10 || 4 || 6 || 0 || .400 ||